  Then there exists a random variable $U$ such that
$$  d[U;U] + \alpha \sum_{i=1}^n d[Y_i;U] \leq \Bigl(2 + \frac{\alpha n}{2} \Bigr) \delta + \alpha \sum_{i=1}^n d[Y_i;T_2].
$$
-/
